title: Joint Strike Fighter.iso
description:
A flight simulator made by Innerloop from Norway, basing itself on two specific multi-role stealth aircrafts, the Lockheed X35, and the Boeing X32, which are the two playable aircrafts. The game features four non-linear campaigns, never-seen-before weapons, up to 8 players, weather effects and more.

Mount with Daemon tools, install, and play!

If you download, please SEED!
